      "content": "it's just... it doesn't feel like it'll ever get better. i look at the empty side of the bed and i just feel this massive weight. like, why am i even struggling so hard to stay here? it feels more like a chore than living. does it ever actually stop feeling like this, or is this just what it is now? just an endless, empty loop?",
